Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.25,0:01:41.73,Tensei op CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(280,250)}碰触到的指尖会疼痛受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.73,0:01:45.85,Tensei op JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(280,250)}大切なもの 要らないもの{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.73,0:01:45.85,Tensei op CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(280,250)}举足轻重 抑或无关痛痒
